        <title>FAIR RATES Act of 2019</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the Federal Insurance Office of the Department of the Treasury to conduct a study to identify disparities between communities in auto insurance costs and payout amounts based on the predominant racial makeup of such communities, and for other purposes.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
